r />\n好似<br />\n睇中(zung3/jung3)<br />\n中(zung3/jung3)獎<br />\n正中(zung3/jung3)下懷<br />\n<br />\n中字喺解位置先會讀第一聲zung1/jung1。<br />\n好似<br />\n中(zung1/jung1)間<br />\n中(zung1/jung1)學<br />\n萬中(zung1/jung1)無一<br />\n<br />\n所以中意要讀第三聲中(zung3/jung3)意（即「眾意」），都唔係廣東話普遍嘅發音，所以我偏向鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肥絲博學<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcjcJWeyCmyHQbQrEhKj9djNNXHVne5mpyoUFq8mJBcoQ?filename=s1Eq5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs1Eq5.gif&h=815772c6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcjcJWeyCmyHQbQrEhKj9djNNXHVne5mpyoUFq8mJBcoQ?filename=s1Eq5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs1Eq5.gif&h=815772c6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcjcJWeyCmyHQbQrEhKj9djNNXHVne5mpyoUFq8mJBcoQ?filename=s1Eq5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs1Eq5.gif&h=815772c6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcjcJWeyCmyHQbQrEhKj9djNNXHVne5mpyoUFq8mJBcoQ?filename=s1Eq5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs1Eq5.gif&h=815772c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04dedffd3dd3af2351ce8a5cd029a8cfb3ec66b9","tid":58303,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個中字如果解作合意時要讀第三聲zung3/jung3。<br />\n好似<br />\n睇中(zung3/jung3)<br />\n中(zung3/jung3)獎<br />\n正中(zung3/jung3)下懷<br />\n<br />\n中字喺解位置先會讀第一聲zung1/jung1。<br />\n好似<br />\n中(zung1/jung1)間<br />\n中(zung1/jung1)學<br />\n萬中(zung1/jung1)無一<br />\n<br />\n所以中意要讀第三聲中(zung3/jung3)意（即「眾意」），都唔係廣東話普遍嘅發音，所以我偏向鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁意思上兩隻字係咪有差異<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afa4cdb5ec082f6045d90a1a89841fd942f948b","tid":58303,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,